text:
Hiya
I need to create a module displaying summaries other blogs above my main blog listing template.
I've created a module and can add the 'blog' snippets but this just shows the blog ID. I want to do something like this
```{% for item in module.news %}
  {{ item }} // just prints blog id
  {{ item.featured_image }}
  {{ item.name }}
  {{ item.post_list_content }}
{% endfor %}```
